<p
  style="color:#4b5563;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;"
>Hola {{firstName}},</p>
<h2
  style="color:#1a1a1a;margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;"
>Verificacion de cuenta</h2>
<p
  style="color:#4b5563;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 24px 0;font-size:16px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;"
>Verifique su cuenta para completar el proceso de registro.</p>
<table
  cellpadding='0'
  cellspacing='0'
  border='0'
  width='100%'
  style='width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;margin-bottom:24px;mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;'
>
  <tr>
    <td
      style="padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#6b7280;font-size:14px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;text-align:left;vertical-align:top;width:40%"
    >Nombre</td>
    <td
      style="padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:14px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;text-align:left;vertical-align:top"
    >{{firstName}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      style="padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#6b7280;font-size:14px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;text-align:left;vertical-align:top;width:40%"
    >Apellido</td>
    <td
      style="padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:14px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;text-align:left;vertical-align:top"
    >{{lastName}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      style="padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#6b7280;font-size:14px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;text-align:left;vertical-align:top;width:40%"
    >Correo electronico</td>
    <td
      style="padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:14px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;text-align:left;vertical-align:top"
    >{{email}}</td>
  </tr>
</table>